snippet.title: Range is HOT! - Rifle Range 01 Walkthrough
snippet.description: In this video we go over the basics of playing a new course in Range is HOT! Walk the course. Familiarize yourself with sections and targets. Practice your skill and compete for top gun on the leaderboard with the lowest score. Available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1503590/Range_is_HOT/
